name: Daily_Run
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily jog
des: Are you a runner?! If you are and don't have a set schedule then this skill is for you. All you need to do is tell Alexa "daily jog" and she will tell you how many miles to run between 0-10.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
